<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1171.104142.figure20>
    dc:description "Figure 20. Aedeagi of the Novochares sallaei species group A-E N. chaquensis F N. garciai G-I N. dicranospathus J-L N. atratus M-R N. sallaei A-C Argentina D Costa Rica E Trinidad M-P Guatemala Q, R Mexico A, D-G, J, M, Q dorsal view B, H, K, N, R ventral view C, I, L, O lateral view P oblique view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/881187" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1171.104142.figure23>
    dc:description "Figure 23. Distribution of Novochares sallaei species group. N. sallaei (red: circles, examined specimens; squares, literature / unconfirmed records), N. guadelupensis (yellow), N. yanomami (blue), N. kawsay (green)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/881190" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1171.104142.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Aedeagi of the Novochares punctatostriatus, Novochares sallaei, and Novochares orchis species groups along with schematic representations of the whole, the parameres (in blue), and the dorsal (in yellow) and ventral (in red) plates of the median lobe A N. dentatus B N. orchis C N. sallaei." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/881171" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

